description:
In this video, Adam will show you how to paint the MV44 Oversight Drone that accompanies the Vespid Stingwings kill team. Follow along to see how to quickly paint your own Oversight Drone and get it ready for high intensity battles in the killzones of the 41st Millennium in no time at all! 

Here is a list of the paints we’ll be using:

Base
Khorne Red
Leadbelcher
Mechanicus Standard Grey

Layer
Dawnstone
Dryad Bark
Gorthor Brown
White Scar

Contrast
Black Legion
Frostheart
Skeleton Horde

Shade
Nuln Oil

Technical 
Lahmian Medium

If you're new to painting, our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials playlist hosts an array of beginner-friendly videos to help you get started.
